1100
01:40:50,498 --> 01:40:53,284
I don't know...

1101
01:40:53,584 --> 01:40:56,585
It's all so difficult.

1102
01:40:58,588 --> 01:41:02,455
I don't want to live with anyone other than you.

1103
01:41:11,601 --> 01:41:14,554
