1128
01:43:09,542 --> 01:43:12,957
I do my best ...

1129
01:43:25,306 --> 01:43:28,306
Okay, I'll sit here...

1130
01:43:31,478 --> 01:43:36,354
I'm sitting here and you can read to me.

1131
01:43:36,650 --> 01:43:42,770
