1145
01:45:43,349 --> 01:45:47,596
“Yesterday I was overcome by a carefree cheerfulness.”

1146
01:45:47,895 --> 01:45:52,556
For the first time this year, I felt joy in life.

1147
01:45:52,857 --> 01:45:56,606
“I’m excited to see what the day will bring.”

1148
01:45:56,903 --> 01:45:58,860
And so forth...

1149
01:46:00,989 --> 01:46:02,982
