1150
01:46:05,911 --> 01:46:10,786
“I turned around and looked at the photo of my class at school.”

1151
01:46:11,917 --> 01:46:14,489
taken when I was 10.

1152
01:46:14,794 --> 01:46:20,914
I seemed to discover something I had missed before.

1153
01:46:22,260 --> 01:46:26,422
To my surprise, I have to admit,

1154
01:46:26,722 --> 01:46:30,422
I don't know who I am.

1155
01:46:31,100 --> 01:46:33,307
Not at all...

1156
01:46:34,812 --> 01:46:39,521
I always did what I was told.

1157
01:46:39,817 --> 01:46:41,608
As far as I can remember,

1158
01:46:42,278 --> 01:46:47,948
I was obedient, balanced, almost gentle.

1159
01:46:48,241 --> 01:46:55,203
I have asserted myself as a girl once or twice,

1160
01:46:55,498 --> 01:47:01,002
but Mother punished all such violations of the Convention

1161
01:47:01,294 --> 01:47:05,162
with exemplary rigor.

1162
01:47:05,673 --> 01:47:09,007
My entire upbringing

1163
01:47:09,302 --> 01:47:14,296
aimed to make me agreeable.

1164
01:47:14,598 --> 01:47:17,931
I was ugly and clumsy.

1165
01:47:18,227 --> 01:47:22,604
A fact I was constantly reminded of.

1166
01:47:22,898 --> 01:47:28,188
But if I kept my thoughts to myself

1167
01:47:28,486 --> 01:47:32,649
and was ingratiating,

1168
01:47:32,948 --> 01:47:36,780
my behavior was rewarded.

1169
01:47:37,620 --> 01:47:43,824
