1170
01:47:44,126 --> 01:47:49,914
All my thoughts revolved around sex.

1171
01:47:50,715 --> 01:47:55,257
But I never told my parents that,

1172
01:47:55,552 --> 01:47:58,672
or anyone for that matter.

1173
01:47:59,431 --> 01:48:03,476
Be deceitful and mysterious

1174
01:48:03,769 --> 01:48:08,264
has become second nature to me.

1175
01:48:08,564 --> 01:48:11,814
My father wanted me to become a lawyer like him.

1176
01:48:12,568 --> 01:48:17,064
I said I wanted to be an actress,

1177
01:48:17,364 --> 01:48:22,784
or do something else in the theatre world,

1178
01:48:23,078 --> 01:48:25,200
but they laughed at me.

1179
01:48:25,496 --> 01:48:29,115
Since then I've been pretending.

1180
01:48:29,417 --> 01:48:32,453
A deception in my relationships with others.

1181
01:48:32,753 --> 01:48:35,291
For men.

1182
01:48:35,589 --> 01:48:38,127
The same deception -

1183
01:48:38,425 --> 01:48:42,125
a desperate attempt to please.

1184
01:48:43,346 --> 01:48:47,558
I never thought about what I wanted.

1185
01:48:47,850 --> 01:48:54,683
Only: “What does he want me to think?”

1186
01:48:54,982 --> 01:48:59,311
It is not selflessness, as I always believed,

1187
01:48:59,611 --> 01:49:02,814
but pure cowardice.

1188
01:49:03,114 --> 01:49:07,064
It comes from the fact that I don't know who I am.

1189
01:49:07,702 --> 01:49:12,696
Our mistake was that we did not break away from our families.

1190
01:49:12,999 --> 01:49:19,332
“and to create something valuable according to our own ideas.”

1191
01:50:01,084 --> 01:50:03,160
Oh damn, I fell asleep!

1192
01:50:03,461 --> 01:50:07,044
