1194
01:50:14,513 --> 01:50:20,633
I'm not offended, but I think you should go home now.

1195
01:50:20,936 --> 01:50:23,936
Yes, I'd better go.

1196
01:50:28,443 --> 01:50:34,729
Please call, if only for the sake of the children.

1197
01:50:35,032 --> 01:50:40,073
- You're always welcome here. - If only Paula wasn't so jealous.

1198
01:50:40,370 --> 01:50:43,786
Nevertheless, she has good reasons …

1199
01:50:44,582 --> 01:50:48,626
- When will you hear about the USA? - In about a month.

1200
01:50:48,919 --> 01:50:53,580
- Let me know how it went. - Of course I'll call you.

1201
01:50:53,883 --> 01:50:58,425
We need to be clear about the divorce.

1202
01:50:58,720 --> 01:51:02,254
- Do you want to get married again? - I don't know.

1203
01:51:02,556 --> 01:51:06,720
