1236
01:57:02,844 --> 01:57:07,422
If you're so attached to it, keep it, but it's mine.

1237
01:57:07,724 --> 01:57:11,887
You're always right, aren't you? Take the damn watch!

1238
01:57:12,562 --> 01:57:17,851
